    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748110/extras/2a25daa06973eb39dff0b426af42b3c6.avif?t=1772049570\" width=624 height=250 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748110/extras/bc4f8335d762eb3e711010b48d20559f.poster.avif?t=1772049570\" width=620 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748110/extras/bc4f8335d762eb3e711010b48d20559f.webm?t=1772049570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748110/extras/bc4f8335d762eb3e711010b48d20559f.mp4?t=1772049570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收到父母的来信后，伊藤不情愿地回到家乡，帮助家里打理农场和经营餐馆。当他重新融入家庭生活时，伊藤意识到这个曾经平静的村庄隐藏着一个古老的秘密，而这个小镇需要他的帮助去揭开其禁忌的过去，以及萦绕在他们心头的阴云。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748110/extras/ba7213b9e12a1da35a8f6280ec535519.avif?t=1772049570\" width=624 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748110/extras/30e54ac258f5843688e291d0ecf61f4e.poster.avif?t=1772049570\" width=620 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748110/extras/30e54ac258f5843688e291d0ecf61f4e.webm?t=1772049570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748110/extras/30e54ac258f5843688e291d0ecf61f4e.mp4?t=1772049570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索佐兹的周围地区和帮助镇民的过程中，你可以利用伊藤的技能和他可靠的砍刀，与几位忠诚的同伴一起组队，砍杀并躲避敌人。每个人都会使用自己独特的技能来击败敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748110/extras/9f836c61f1859f5c0e552a48153350d9.avif?t=1772049570\" width=624 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748110/extras/82e8784e96d48c70e2d73ab40f35ee08.poster.avif?t=1772049570\" width=620 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748110/extras/82e8784e96d48c70e2d73ab40f35ee08.webm?t=1772049570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748110/extras/82e8784e96d48c70e2d73ab40f35ee08.mp4?t=1772049570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在佐兹，食物是通往人心中的道路，给镇民送上他们最爱的食物将增加你们的感情，让你得以更加了解他们。或者，你也可以自己吃掉这些食物，为下次狩猎获得强大的属性加成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748110/extras/ea845c04f2c5007ff87f99f6601a266f.avif?t=1772049570\" width=624 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748110/extras/f4834fc7128ceb1fbf3057dd9ebe4624.poster.avif?t=1772049570\" width=620 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748110/extras/f4834fc7128ceb1fbf3057dd9ebe4624.webm?t=1772049570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748110/extras/f4834fc7128ceb1fbf3057dd9ebe4624.mp4?t=1772049570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个人都有自己的故事，而伊藤必须掌握灵魂灌注砍刀和魔法灌注食谱，才能帮助他们克服个人的噩梦。帮助传奇的小镇英雄、时尚店主、邦波拉队的明星、当地魔法教派的领袖，并与能将魔法注入武器和工具的灵魂铁匠交谈。</p>",
